 process for\nSMEs by removing ambiguity in regards to fundamentals associated with their\norganisation and cloud adoption process.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 Jan 2016 17:21:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-01-08"}
