tronic part, reproducing the experimental total specific heat at and below\n$T_c$ within a $5 \\%$ error range, from which the cubic ($\\ss T^3$) term for\nlow temperatures is obtained. In addition, we show that this model reproduces\nthe cuprates mass anisotropies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 Jan 2016 20:34:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-05-04"}
