 projected\nWFIRST orbit. Performance degradation due to radiation displacement damage is\nreported, which is the first such study for a CCD201-20 that replicates the\nWFIRST conditions. In addition, techniques intended to identify and mitigate\nradiation-induced electron trapping, such as trap pumping, custom clocking, and\nthermal cycling, are discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 Jan 2016 03:23:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-01-11"}
